de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter

Interface Exporter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.pf4j.ExtensionPoint, OpenDiabetesPlugin
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractExporter, CSVFileExporter, FileExporter, MLExporter, OdvDbJsonExporter.OdvDbJsonExporterImplementation, ODVExporter.ODVExporterImplementation, PlotterExporter.PlotterExporterImplementation, SliceLayoutCSVExporter.SliceLayoutCSVExporterImplementation, SourceCodeExporter.SourceCodeExporterImplementation, VaultCSVExporter.VaultCSVExporterImplementation, VaultExporter

    public interface Exporter
extends org.pf4j.ExtensionPoint, OpenDiabetesPlugin
    This interface specifies the methods shared by all exporters. Furthermore it serves as the ExtensionPoint where the plugins hook up. Thus all exporter plugins must implement this interface to get recognized as exporters.

    • Method Detail

      • setEntries

        void setEntries(java.util.List<?> entries)
         throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        This method is used to set the entries to export. Should only be used with exporters that do not export from VaultEntry but something different like SliceEntry.
        Parameters:
        entries - The entries which will be exported by the respective exporter.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - Thrown if the wrong kind of entries were set.

        Parameters:
